'''Hired Gun'''是由[[Xbox游戏工作室|微軟遊戲工作室]]内部创建的一个中等规模开发小组。该小组的工作《[[光环2|光环2]]》从原来的[[Xbox_(游戏机)|Xbox]]版本转移到[[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]版本。从2006年2月初至2007年4月进行名为“光晕2 Vista”或“H2V”的项目，负责人为Jo Clowes。2007年10月团队解散，并在微軟遊戲工作室分配到的其他项目上。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://forums.haloonwindowsvista.com/forums/3/6084/ShowThread.aspx |title=Halo On Windows Vista - was that a patch |date=2007-11-06 |quote=Correct, the Hired Gun team no longer exists, but that doesn't necessarily mean all support has been dropped. All it means is that I no longer know about any future patches, etc. |publisher=[[Microsoft_Studios_(game_studio)|Halo 2 on Windows Vista forums]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080820093927/http://forums.haloonwindowsvista.com/forums/3/6084/ShowThread.aspx |archivedate=2008-08-20 |accessdate=2015-11-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://hushedcasket.com/node/2632|title=First FASA. Now Hired Gun, makers of Halo 2 Vista, no longer exists.|date=2007-11-12|publisher=the Hushed Casket|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110521192912/http://hushedcasket.com/node/2632|archivedate=2011-05-21|accessdate=2015-11-20}}</ref>

